p: Petition for a writ of Habeas Corpus In the consistent court of of the 3rd Judicial District of Washington Territory city of Seattle in and for the counties of King and Kitsah. In the matter of the application of Donald Fallon Frank Rogers for a writ of Habeas Corpus Petition for writ. To the Hon. J. R. Lewis Chief Justice of the Supreme Court of Washington Territory and Judge of the said 3rd Judicial District The petition of Donald Fallon and Frank Rogers Shows that they said Donald Fallon and Frank Rogers and unlawfully imprisioned detained confined and restrained of their liberties by Louis V. Wyckoff
